2D-ROESY and NOESY are also used to ascertain the ring fusion type . ROE/NOE correlations between CH 3 -19/H-4 b , CH 3 -19/H-8, CH 3 -18/H-8 and CH 3 -18/H-20 confirm A/B trans , B/C trans C/D trans and D/E cis- fusions, respectively. Further , correlations between H-14/H-16 and -17 give evidence for cis -fused D/E rings (
