)
.

NOE and NOESY techniques are also used to determine the stereochemistry at position 25. In case of 39 , the R -configuration was deduced by the NOE correlation of 27-methyl with H-26 eq./ax. and H-24 ax. (
). Similarly, the correlation of H-25 with H-23ax. gave indication about the R -configuration in 40 (
).

